# Copy this file to ".env.local" and fill in your APS app's Client ID.
#
# This is a PUBLIC client identifier for a "Desktop, Mobile, Single-Page App"
# type APS app — it is NOT a secret (it is visible in the browser during the
# PKCE login). We still keep it in .env.local (gitignored) so the repo stays
# portable across different APS apps / environments.
#
# Vite only exposes variables prefixed with VITE_ to the browser, and only
# reads env files at dev-server startup — restart `npm run dev` after editing.
VITE_APS_CLIENT_ID=
